## ✨ About

**E-Commerce Portfolio** is a responsive personal website built to present an e-commerce professional in a clean, modern, and elegant way.

The website highlights his profile, experience, skills, services, and professional work with a strong visual identity.

---

## 🎨 Features

- Modern and clean UI design
- Fully responsive layout
- Professional hero section
- Skills and services showcase
- Smooth user experience
- Portfolio-style presentation
- Built with modern web technologies

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

<div align="center">

| Technology | Usage |
| ---------- | ----- |
| **Next.js** | Website framework |
| **React** | UI components |
| **Tailwind CSS** | Styling and layout |
| **HTML / CSS** | Structure and design |

</div>

---

